        h1 Hawaii Annual Code Challenge
        p Governor David Ige, the Office of Enterprise Technology Services (ETS), and the State of Hawaii Transformation Internship Programs (TIP) hosted the Hawaii Annual Code Challenge (HACC). The Hawaii Annual Code Challenge was a month-long event to solve problems that the state currently faces. Departments discussed their current problems, and the groups had to creatively find solutions.
